Stdio MCP servers via --mcp-config never worked with Claude CLI. The CLI received the JSON but silently failed to connect. Fix: use create_sdk_mcp_server() to run xpressclaw tools in-process instead of as a subprocess. The harness detects mcp_xpressclaw in the args and creates an SDK server with @tool decorators wrapping each handler. This is the recommended approach per the Agent SDK docs.
